name: Rian Dawson
bio: boom boom bang bang crash for all time low.

social_posts.post_text: That’s a wrap on 2022. Briefly put - every second on stage with these lovely men is a gd gift. I love you boys. Here’s to 2023… thank you atl fam, our collective heart beats FOR YOU! 📷 @_lupe da goat.

Happy birthday to the absolute love of my life. How you share so much of your light with everyone and still have enough left to be the person you are is incredible. Thank you for changing my life for the better every day, I’ll never forget how damn lucky i am spend it with you, I love you I love you I love you.

2023 is off to a hell of a start. Tell Me I’m Alive (the song) is out now! Tell Me I’m Alive (the album) is out March 17. Tons of tour announcements. Damn let’s go! Big shouts to @alexgaskarth for jumping in the directors chair for this video, he absolutely killed it along with @djaybrawner . It’s a ton of prep work and even more work days of the shoots, and remained pretty damn in control. Well done my lad. Enjoy the ride folks, we’ll see you soon. Also did @zacharymerrick crush his role or what. Sexiest devil award. Okay enough coffee talk. All photos by the amazingly talented @salmabustos

20 years in and I still am the luckiest to explore the world with by best buds. Spain&France you were amazing, onto Zurich tonight then Germany! Cold brew game strong in Switzerland btw. All photos @_lupe the creator.
WEIGHTLESS INTO MONSTERS TRANSITION MAKES ME FEEL. video from our show in Munich! @_lupe on the lens & @scratchcardphil making it sound pretty. (Ok @stevehussein on the assist too)

Just a smattering of euro pics thus far. I’m having so much fun, not messing up a lot, and all the boys and girls in the band and crew are just killing it. so stoked we still have a lot of road left to travel. love y’all :) all good pics by @_lupe 🐐
Watching the crowd bounce during Sleepwalking gives me the big smiles. Nothing crazy on drums, just fun to groove and go boom boom bang. What else would y’all want to see from the set?
Europe continues to just be amazing. Love y’all. 3x flat whites daily. Netherlands tonight, Belgium tomorrow. LETS GOOOOO. Happiness by @_lupe

no words. capping off a tour + starting a new record cycle at a sold out wembley. we are just getting started. love you all, love you so damn much. thank you from the bottom of my heart. tell me im alive out now and on tour forever. pics by the greatest ever, @_lupe

Either I was smiling the entire day yesterday at @sunfest or @thomasfalcone only snapped me when I was straight cheese. Great time yesterday in west palm. LA this weekend, then rehearsals then TOUR. Ryman, red rocks, let’s go people. Ok fine, all smiles here.

Hi we started a band in 9th grade in my parents basement and just played a sold out show at @theryman and are doing the same at @redrocksco in a few days :) hope you’re happy everyone. Cold brew and water. All visual goodness by the incredible  @_lupe and @salmabustos
Mostly how much I love my gorgeous girlfriend. Also other things I love. Happy spring everyone. See you on the road. I’m gonna bring my airstream on tour this fall.

Always a fun time crafting new drums for @riandawson & we this time we had the opportunity to match the new @alltimelow album artwork. Thank you Rian for your support of #sjcdrums for over 15 years! ❤️

Hit the website for more details and specs on Rian’s new kit, pick up their new album, and catch them on the road now!

#sjcfamily #customdrums #alltimelow
We sold out red rocks in 2 weeks. This can’t be real. All love to you ATL family. Thanks for letting me live a dream every day. 📸 @_lupe @salmabustos
You are my sunshine. You constantly turn my world into a beautiful day. I love you Sav. Mushy.
touring drumming camming rose-ing. Sav using Steve as a step to get into truck. Life is good. Love you all :) thanks @salmabustos for being such a badass.

Feeling refreshed and more grateful than ever to be in this band. Thank you all for one of my favorite tours, thank you for looking out for one another at the shows, thank you for spreading love and happiness and laughing at those who don’t. All Time Low FOREVER. @salmabustos you are a damn queen in front of and behind the lens.
Fun one offs gigs. Lotta smiles. Getting excited for fall tour prep, setlist building all that jazz. Going on a 4 week camp trip first. Love you!
AI is gonna change everything 🤖

OKAY WE’RE ROLLING NOW. First show rescheduled due to wet+electricity, Boston welcomed us with open arms. Hell of a show, hell of a venue. Sound of Letting Go tour coming to a city near you GET THERE. Love you all. @salmabustos u crazy behind the lens.
New York what the hell that was an insane show. Love that venue, love your city, love you peeeeeeople. Stumptown cold brew is everywhere there, awesome. Hugs. @salmabustos with the fire.

Six in a row @ 23ish songs per show my bones are not happy with me. So damn proud of this show, hope yall are loving it as much as we are. See you tomorrow MONTREAL then TORONTO let’s go. 

@salmabustos you are capture queen.
A few of my favorite people :)
I think spindrift is the best flavored sparkling water, but probably drink more la croix due to availability. Bubbly is up there. Dammit but then topo twist of lime too. Thoughts?
Little bit of Monsters from Chitown. Yes I’ve watched The Bear and yes I have a crush on Jeremy Allen White.

Had the best summer of my life with the best human in my life. Took the airstream for 5 weeks, many states, many national parks, many miles on the truck.  Sav got a film camera  and shot these as a first timer, so rad. Love you so much and so thankful to have you as a partner on this ride ❤️

Surprisingly not an ad just a few dudes being dudes and having a shop. I love you Pacific Northwest. Wrapping up this tour and I’m sad and not ready for it to end. Thank you all, my heart is full. All pics by @salmabustos
Another tour wrapped. So damn grateful for the bands and the fans, feeling so warm n fuzzy heading into When We Were Young ❤️. Here’s the end of the set, captured by queen @salmabustos

I’m sure I’ll have at LEAST one more post about WWWY fest, and I’m still coming down from the whole experience, but here’s sleepwalking for the time being. For those who ask if I still get nervous, a resounding YES. Love to you all, I’m gonna run amuck with my lady and my dog for a few days before Australia!
Australia how I’ve missed your freaky little creatures and amazing coffee. Great start in Perth, see you tomorrow Adelaide. Oi Oi Oi.

Hey Fellas! Remember when we started the band in my parents basement and said “yeah 20 years from now we’ll be headlining a sold out arena gig in the furthest country from where we are right now”? Yeah me neither. Thank you Melbourne, unforgettable. One of my favorite parts of the set here from New Religion. Cheeky cymbal choke in the middle.

Two more shows in Australia before I hibernate for a month. Here’s what I’ll say:  cold brew here is FANTASTIC but let’s get some bigger cups yeah? Can’t be ordering 6x a day you’ll make me feel addicted…wait…
Hugs n Kisses n Chokes. Thanks for letting me travel the world and do the boomboomka with my absolute best friends. Back home to hibernate 😵‍💫😴
HEROES from my point of view. What a fun one, but damn this being at the end of our “Act 1” after 6 in a row got my heart rate MOVING. from our sold out show in Sydney 🤯🤯🤯

20 years of stupid boys making basement noise 🖤 Bonus shows are SOLD OUT and tickets for Red Rocks, Salt Shed, and Merriweather are moving FAST so don’t miss out!! Thanks for kicking off the celebration with us… AllTimeLow.com for tickets #AllTimeLowForever

06.04 - Morrison, CO @ Red Rocks Amphitheatre
07.26 - Chicago, IL @ The Salt Shed
08.24 - Columbia, MD @ Merriweather Post Pavilion
Still wondering how we got this far… #AllTimeLowForever

Damn. What a way to ring in 2024. Played the @ravens v Dolphins game, and it was a spanking. The game, not the show. Sorry dolphin friends. Stoked for what’s to come. I’m hibernating. Love you all. ❤️. Pics by @nickalausstafford

Sometimes you’re lucky in life to have people that share their light. Sometimes people sneak in that block your light. Somehow, I won the lottery and fell in love with a human that, purely, IS my light.
You are my love now and always Sav, thank you for making me a better partner, a better friend, and a better man. My heart is yours. Happy Birthday :)
